[h3 
	" Who is 
	(__wikiLink|TASVideoAgent)
	"?
	$LF
]h3
[p 
	"TAS Video Agent is a humble drone of 
	(__wikiLink|user:Nach)
	", created on 2009-07-03.
	$LF
	"It is written in C using standard UNIX sockets and pipes, for the new server.
	$LF
]p
[h4 
	" TAS Video Agent
	$LF
]h4
[p 
	"Its primary purpose is to sit on the 
	(__wikiLink|IRC Channel)
	$LF
	"and report on everything that happens on
	$LF
	"the 
	[a href=/forum/ 
		"discussion forums
	]a
	".
	$LF
]p
[p 
	"It also tells us when new submissions have been made or new movies
	$LF
	"have been published.
	$LF
]p
[p 
	"TAS Video Agent originally was not very reliable. Since bug fixes made on 2011-04-05, TAS Video Agent is extremely stable.
	$LF
]p
[pre 
	"<
	(__wikiLink|user:Velitha)
	"> TASVA, your connection is about as stable as my computer used to be before I got my SSD :P
	$LF
	"<TASVideoAgent> Velitha: nonsense!  My connection is as stable as the economy!
	$LF
]pre
[p 
	"Since October 2012, TASVideoAgent also sits in 
	[a class=extlink href=http://webchat.freenode.net/?channels=#tasemu rel=nofollow 
		"#tasemu on FreeNode
	]a
	". Where development 
	[a href=/EmulatorResources 
		"of our rerecording emulators
	]a
	" is discussed, and all 
	[a href=/EmulatorResources/Updates 
		"changes
	]a
	" are announced live, as they happen.
	$LF
]p
